<div class="mf-section-0" id="mf-section-0">
<p>Homeschooling can feel like uncharted territory, particularly if youre adapting to the COVID-19 pandemic. Its completely normal to feel stressed, uncertain, and overwhelmed about the days to come. While homeschooling can be a bit unpredictable at times, you can put your best foot forward by developing a simple routine and not putting too much pressure on yourself or your kids.
</p>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
