<div class="section tips sticky">
<h2 class="section-heading" onclick="javascript:mfTempOpenSection(2)">
<div class="altblock"></div>
<div class="mw-ui-icon mw-ui-icon-element indicator"></div>
<span class="mw-headline" id="Tips">Tips</span>
</h2>
<div id="tips" class="section_text">
<ul>
<li><div>Talk with your child and work toward creating a successful routine.<sup id="_ref-16" class="reference trusted" aria-label="Link to Reference 16"><a href="#_note-16">[16]</a><span class="ts_popup trustedsource" hidden id="ts_popup_16" style="display: none;">
	<span class="ts_close">X</span>
		<a class="ts_trustworthy" href="/wikiHow:Delivering-a-Trustworthy-Experience">Trustworthy Source</a>

		<span class="ts_name">Greater Good Magazine</span>
		<span class="ts_description">Journal published by UC Berkeley's Greater Good Science Center, which uses scientific research to promote happier living</span>

				<a href="#" class="ts_source" target="_blank">Go to source</a>
</span></sup><div class="clearall"></div>
</div>
<div class="wh_vote_container">
	<span class="wh_thumb_response wh_thumb_msg">Thanks!</span>
	<div>
		<a href="#" class="trvote_up_b52ccb8639ac8cede18e8eea862e9c38_1 vote_up wh_vote_box">
			Helpful
			<span class="tr_vote">1</span>
		</a>
		<a href="#" class="trvote_down_b52ccb8639ac8cede18e8eea862e9c38_1 vote_down wh_vote_box">
			Not Helpful
			<span class="tr_vote">0</span>
		</a>
	</div>
</div>


</li>
<li><div>Encourage your kids to Zoom chat with any friends who are also being home-schooled.<sup id="_ref-17" class="reference" aria-label="Link to Reference 17"><a href="#_note-17">[17]</a><span class="ts_popup " hidden id="ts_popup_17" style="display: none;">
	<span class="ts_close">X</span>
		<span class="ts_name">Research source</span>
		<span class="ts_description"></span>
				<a href="#" class="ts_source" target="_blank"></a>

</span></sup><div class="clearall"></div>
</div>
<div class="wh_vote_container">
	<span class="wh_thumb_response wh_thumb_msg">Thanks!</span>
	<div>
		<a href="#" class="trvote_up_cc1f001d2417c7a2669642f94cfb8f3b_1 vote_up wh_vote_box">
			Helpful
			<span class="tr_vote">1</span>
		</a>
